comments.body:
Is this the suggested way to use this API?

```
import * as UserCard from './app/ui/client/lib/UserCard';
```

I remember @sampaiodiego saying something about using the upmost module to be used as an interface, therefore:

```
// 1st option
import { UserCard } from './app/ui/client';
// 2nd option
import { openUserCard, closeUserCard } from './app/ui/client';
```

This can't be done with named exports here.

